  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: TOTAL COST - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
    <dl>
      <dlentry>
        <dt>Format / Length</dt>
        <dd>max n18.max n8</dd>
      </dlentry>
    </dl>

  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_total_cost">TOTAL COST</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_financial_amount">FINANCIAL AMOUNT</xref>
 for use in 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/contract_monitoring.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Contract_Monitoring</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_total_cost">TOTAL COST</xref>
 is the total cost of an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>
 and/or financial adjustment that includes any agreed adjustment e.g. 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/market_forces_factor.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Market_Forces_Factor</xref>
, Best Practice Tariff, Value Added Tax, home delivery charge where appropriate.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_total_cost">TOTAL COST</xref>
 should be calculated in accordance with 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/national_tariff_payment_system.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">National_Tariff_Payment_System</xref>
 guidance, which can be on the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 website at: 
    <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/resources/pay-syst/"
            scope="external"
            format="html">NHS Payment System Guidance</xref>
.  </p>


